n). Uses `ProfileBloc`, `SwAvatar`, `SwGenderSelector`, `SwBottomSheet`.\n- **`p
rofile_edit_page.dart`** — Full profile editor with extended info (bio, tags, pr
eferred gender, age range, photo grid). Uses `SwTagChip`, `SwRangeSlider`, `SwPh
otoGrid`.\n\n### 2. BLoCs / Cubits\nLocated in `apps/mobile/lib/presentation/blo
cs/`:\n- **`auth/auth_bloc.dart`** — Manages login/logout/auth-check. States: `A
uthUnauthenticated`, `AuthAuthenticating`, `AuthAuthenticated(isNewUser, profile
Complete)`, `AuthFailure`. Uses `equatable`.\n- **`profile/profile_bloc.dart`** 
— Handles load/save/update/upload/reorder/delete for profile. States: `ProfileIn
itial`, `ProfileLoading`, `ProfileLoaded`, `ProfileComplete`, `ProfileError`.\n-
**`dev_tools/dev_tools_cubit.dart`** — Simple `Cubit` for dev-tools server URL c
onfig (load/validate/save).\n\n### 3. Routing (go_router)\nConfigured in `apps/m
obile/lib/app.dart`:\n- `GoRouter` with `initialLocation: \'/login\'`.\n- Routes
: `/login`, `/home`, `/profile-setup`, `/profile-edit`.\n- `BlocListener<AuthBlo
c>` listens to auth state and programmatically navigates:\n  - Authenticated + i
ncomplete profile → `/profile-setup`\n  - Authenticated + complete profile → `/h
ome`\n  - Unauthenticated / Failure → `/login`\n- `DevToolsWrapper` wraps the ap
p in debug mode.\n\n### 4. Repositories & Datasources Structure\nClean architect
ure pattern with abstract domain + data implementation:\n- **Domain contracts**:
`lib/domain/repositories/{auth,profile,dev_tools}_repository.dart`\n- **Implemen
tations**: `lib/data/repositories/{auth,profile,dev_tools}_repository_impl.dart`
\n- **No separate "datasource" layer** — repos call `Dio` directly using generat
ed OpenAPI models.\n- **Auth repo**: login, refresh, logout, getMe. Uses `social
_world_auth_models`.\n- **Profile repo**: get/create/update profile, add/reorder
/delete photo, get upload URL. Uses `social_world_profile_models`.\n- **DevTools
repo**: persists server base URL via `SharedPreferences`.\n\n### 5. Design Syste
m Components\nPackage: `packages/design-system` (imported as `social_world_desig
n_system`).\nAvailable exports:\n- `AppTheme` (light/dark), `DesignTokens` (colo
rs, spacing, font sizes)\n- Atoms: `SwAvatar`, `SwButton`, `SwCard`, `SwTextFiel
d`\n- Molecules: `SwPhotoGrid`, `SwBottomSheet`, `SwGenderSelector`, `SwTagChip`
, `SwRangeSlider`\n\nUsage pattern in pages:\n```dart\nimport \'package:social_w
orld_design_system/social_world_design_system.dart\';\n...\nbackgroundColor: Des
ignTokens.background,\nchild: SwButton(text: \'...\', variant: SwButtonVariant.f
illed, onPressed: ...),\n```\n\n### 6. DI Setup (get_it)\nLocated in `apps/mobil
e/lib/core/di/di.dart`:\n- Uses **manual `get_it` registration** (no `injectable
