nt`, `AuthRepository`, `ProfileRepository`, `SecureStorage`.\n- Factories: `Auth
Bloc`, `ProfileBloc`.\n- Debug-only registrations: `DevToolsRepository`, `DevToo
lsCubit`.\n- `configureDependencies()` called in `main()`.\n\n### 7. Existing Te
sts\nTest dir: `apps/mobile/test/` (4 files):\n- **`login_page_golden_test.dart`
** — Golden tests for initial & loading states. Uses mock `AuthRepository` + `Se
cureStorage`, pumps `MaterialApp` with `BlocProvider.value`, asserts against `go
ldens/login_page_*.png`.\n- **`dev_tools_golden_test.dart`** — Golden tests for 
