, `conversation_id`, `user_id`, `last_read_message_id`, unique `(conversation_id
, user_id)` |\n| `MessageEntity` | `message.entity.ts` | `id`, `conversation_id`
, `sender_id`, `type`, `content`, `client_message_id`, `sequence_id` (bigint, au
to-inc), `status` (default `"sent"`) |\n| `BlockEntity` | `modules/blocks/block.
entity.ts` | `id`, `blocker_id`, `blocked_id`, `reason` |\n\n**Migration:** `app
s/api/src/database/migrations/20250410000000-InitialSchema.ts` creates all table
