e}\'), injects Service\n  {name}.service.ts     // @Injectable(), injects Reposi
tories\n  dto/\n    *.dto.ts            // class-validator decorated classes\n  
{name}.entity.ts      // optional; some use shared entities\n```\n\n**Registrati
on:** Modules are imported into `AppModule` (`apps/api/src/app.module.ts`).\n\n-
