h creation exists yet\n\nThe seed script (`apps/api/src/scripts/seed-dev.ts`) de
monstrates the intended data patterns:\n- `match_actions` rows: `(actor_id, targ
et_id, action)` where action = `"like"` or `"pass"`\n- Mutual likes create a `ma
tches` row, which triggers creation of a `conversations` row + `conversation_par
ticipants` rows\n\n---\n\n### 5. DTO Pattern\n**Location:** `apps/api/src/module
s/*/dto/*.dto.ts`\n\n- **Input DTOs:** Use `class-validator` decorators (`@IsStr
ing`, `@IsOptional`, `@IsNumber`, `@IsEnum`, `@Length`, `@MaxLength`, etc.)\n- *
*Response DTOs:** Often also decorated (sometimes used for Swagger typing), but 
responses are wrapped manually in controllers as `{ code: 0, message: "success",
