rer` token from `Authorization` header\n- Verifies JWT using `jsonwebtoken` + `j
wtConfig.secret`\n- Checks Redis blacklist (`token_blacklist:${jti}`)\n- Attache
s `request.user = { userId: string, jti: string }`\n\n#### `ProfileCompletionGua
rd` (`profile-completion.guard.ts`)\n- Runs after `JwtAuthGuard`\n- Queries `Use
