ies installed** (`apps/api/package.json`):\n- `@nestjs/websockets`\n- `@nestjs/p
latform-socket.io`\n- `socket.io`\n\n**Current state:** **No gateway implementat
ion exists.** There are no `.gateway.ts` files and no WebSocket modules in `apps
/api/src/`. Socket.io is available but completely unused.\n\n---\n\n### Key Impl
ications for Implementing Matching\n\n| Area | Status | Notes |\n|------|-------
-|-------|\n| **Match DB schema** | ✅ Ready | `matches` and `match_actions` tab
les already migrated |\n| **Module scaffolding** | ❌ Missing | Need new `matche
s` module following existing pattern |\n| **Discovery / feed logic** | ❌ Missin
g | Need query to find candidates excluding blocks, existing actions, etc. |\n| 
