e, create `MatchEntity` + `ConversationEntity` + participants |\n| **WebSocket r
eal-time** | ⚠️ Ready to add | Dependencies present but no gateway exists |\n| **
Guards** | ✅ Ready | `JwtAuthGuard` + `ProfileCompletionGuard` can protect matc
hing endpoints |\n| **DTOs / Validation** | ✅ Ready | Follow existing `class-va
lidator` pattern |\n| **UUID generation** | ✅ Ready | Project uses `v7 as uuidv
7` from `uuid` package |\n| **Redis for caching feeds** | ⚠️ Available | Direct `
ioredis` instantiation pattern is established |\n| **Business exceptions** | ✅ 
